text: Reine Wisell (30 September 1941 â€“ 20 March 2022) was a Swedish racing driver. He participated in 23 Formula One World Championship Grands Prix. His career began in 1970 and he retired in 1974. Wisell was born in Motala, Sweden. Wisell died on 20 March 2022 at his home in Thailand from a heart attack at the age of 80. ==References== ==Other websites== *Profile at grandprix.com Category:1941 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Swedish racecar drivers Category:Formula One drivers
